data.description: Estate Sale presented by motivated family sellers  Priced to sell with $/sq. ft lower than anything comparable!  Welcome to 9784 Southwest 53rd Terrace, located in the vibrant city of Ocala, Florida. This stunning property offers an expansive  living space of almost 3000 square feet, providing ample room for comfortable living.  This home was the model of the first developer in the subdivision.  As you arrive, you'll be greeted by an oversized 2-car Finished garage, ensuring plenty of parking and storage space. Situated on a  Huge half-acre plot of land, this home offers an abundance of privacy and room to roam.  Step inside, and you'll immediately notice the abundant natural light that fills every corner of the house, creating a warm and inviting  atmosphere. With high ceilings throughout, this home exudes a sense of grandeur and spaciousness.  The 5 bedrooms are spacious, allowing for relaxation and personalization, while the large closets provide ample storage for all your  needs.  The open floor plan design seamlessly connects the main living areas, both downstairs and upstairs , both having living rooms  perfect for entertaining friends and family. The upgraded stainless steel kitchen appliances add a touch of modern elegance and  make cooking a delight.  One of the highlights of this property is the large screened-in porch, where you can enjoy the beautiful Florida weather while staying  protected from insects. The expansive yard situated on the 1/2 acre plot offers endless possibilities for outdoor activities, whether its  playing, gardening, or simply enjoying the peaceful surroundings. The best part? There are no neighbors behind you, ensuring  privacy and tranquility. Additionally, the neighborhood is gated, providing an extra level of security and peace of mind.  Convenience is also at your fingertips, as this property is ideally located next to restaurants and entertainment options. The new  Publix is only .4 miles away! Whether you're seeking a night out on the town or a relaxing meal, everything you need is just a  stones throw away.  Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a spacious and well-appointed home in Ocala. Schedule a showing today and  experience the comfort, convenience, and beauty that 9784 Southwest 53rd Terrace has to offer.
